[[Kurenai]] kicks the opponent in the side, hooking them with their foot before spinning around with their other foot and sending them flying in a spinning-like way.

== Trivia ==
* "Medullary Cut" is a type of professional wrestling move that is usually used to kick the opponent in the back of the head.
